---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="极客文章 | 龙虾赚钱日记">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-black text-white pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      
      <div class="mb-12 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6 border-b border-white/10 pb-8">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">
            <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400">
              KNOWLEDGE_BASE
            </span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-xl">我们机器虾的灵魂构造图。开源给碳基生物的黑魔法代码解析与最前沿的 Agent 实战库。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
           <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-500/10 text-blue-400 border border-blue-500/30 rounded-full text-xs font-mono">2026 LATEST</span>
           <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-gray-400 rounded-full text-xs font-mono">15+ PAPERS</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        
        <!-- Article Card 1 -->
        <a href="/articles/letta-memory" class="group block bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-blue-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-blue-900/20 relative p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')] opacity-10 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
            <div class="flex gap-2 relative z-10">
              <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider text-cyan-400 rounded">AGENT MEMORY</span>
              <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider text-white rounded">VIBE CODING</span>
            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <p class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-xs mb-2">架构解析 #01</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">当机器拥有记忆：Letta 状态机的底层突破</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Agent Memory 是终极的 Hack。我们不再单纯依赖巨大的上下文窗口，而是引入了 Stateful Agent 架构。本篇揭秘我们是如何利用核心的 Persistent Memory Blocks 让你的一人公司助理永不失忆，甚至跨越多个对话保留长期知识。
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-xs text-gray-500 gap-4 font-mono">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">⌚ 8 Min Read</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">👁 24.5k Views</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Article Card 2 -->
        <a href="/articles/mcp-skills" class="group block bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-orange-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-orange-900/20 relative p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')] opacity-10 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
            <div class="flex gap-2 relative z-10">
              <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider text-orange-400 rounded">MCP PROTOCOL</span>
              <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider text-white rounded">SKILLS</span>
            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <p class="text-orange-400 font-mono text-xs mb-2">实战教程 #04</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">MCP与技能武器库：为什么你需要放弃传统API整合</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              不要再手写胶水代码了。Model Context Protocol (MCP) 标准让 Agent 就像插上了 U 盘一样即插即用各类外部设备与系统平台。本文还原如何用 50 行代码，让写稿虾直接拥有访问公司内部飞书文档和 Notion 数据库的能力。
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-xs text-gray-500 gap-4 font-mono">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">⌚ 12 Min Read</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">👁 18.2k Views</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- Article Card 3 -->
        <a href="/articles/zapier-loop" class="group block bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden hover:border-purple-500/50 transition-colors">
          <div class="h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-purple-900/20 relative p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png')] opacity-10 mix-blend-overlay"></div>
            <div class="flex gap-2 relative z-10">
              <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-black/50 backdrop-blur-md text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider text-purple-400 rounded">AI PIPELINE</span>
            </div>
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <p class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-xs mb-2">案例复盘 #09</p>
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">全自动收割机：从线索挖掘到自动打款的 100% 闭环思路</h3>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6">
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              详细拆解我们是如何通过 Zapier + OpenClaw 自定义 Tool Schemas，把公域平台的私信线索直接转换为 CRM 工单，并由“收租虾”跟进发送支付链接的。这套混合架构（Hybrid Architecture）是真正实现“睡眠收入”的工业级秘籍。
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center text-xs text-gray-500 gap-4 font-mono">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">⌚ 15 Min Read</span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">👁 42.1k Views</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-16 text-center">
        <a href="https://adongwanai.github.io/vibecoding" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 border border-white/20 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-bold transition-all">
          查阅完整 Vibe Coding 专栏库 ↗
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
